Package me.kinomoto.kpub

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Article
    Stores data from database about article, poster or speech.
    ArticleMainView
    JPanel with form for common fields in Article
    Articles
    Stores and manages Articles
    ArticleView
    Settings panel for specific to Article fields
    Author
    Stores author name.
    Connection
    Makes connections with database
    ErrorDialog
    All error messages goes thru this class.
    Filters
    Holds filters status and checks if Article passes all filters.
    Issn
    Stores ISSN – number, name and MNiSW list type.
    IssnAdder
    Form for creating new Issn.
    IssnEditor
    Excel like editor for Issns from IssnModel.
    IssnModel
    Stores and manages all Issn.
    IssnTextEditor
    JFormattedTextField with mask for Issn "####-###*" where '*' can be 0-9X.
    Lang
    Stores language information – ID, English name, Polish name *
    LangEditor
    Excel like editor for LangModel.
    LangModel
    Stores and manages all Langs.
    Main
    Base class for all application.
    OutputFormat
    Stores and manages output format for data.
    OutputFormatEditor
    OutputFormat variables editor
    SpeechPosterView
    Settings panel for specific to Poster/Speech fields
  • Enum Summary

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    Issn.ChecksumException
    threw when checksum of issn number is invalid
    Issn.EmptyNameException
    threw when issn name is empty
    Issn.IssnLenghtException
    threw when issn string is not 9 character long
    Issn.IssnZeroException
    threw when issn is equal to 0000-0000
    Issn.WrongTypeException
    threw when Issn.type can not be cast to Issn.LIST_TYPE
